{"tid":2101608,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【傳最壞情況中行料中銀擠提】內銀擬定對策應付美制裁","createTime":"2020-07-10T02:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T03:11:45.000Z","uid":30040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c610ae6e79e93d2782e93e13f1a3fc47de04ecf8","tid":2101608,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"【傳最壞情況中行料中銀擠提】內銀擬定對策應付美制裁 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3fgqlFy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3fgqlFy&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=a4c44303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3fgqlFy</a><br />\n<br />\n美國除早前通過《#香港自治法案》（Hong Kong Autonomy Act），制裁一系列損害香港自由自治人士外，繼續為其提供服務的銀行亦可能被 #制裁，路透引述消息報道指出，國有內銀包括中國銀行（03988）和工商銀行（01398）等，正就可能被 #禁止使用美元 和美元結算的情況下，擬定相關措施的應急方案，其中，中行預測的最壞情況為旗下中銀香港（02388）可能沒有足夠美元向客戶兌付而造成 #擠提。<br />\n<br />\n據報，國際網絡和海外資產最多的中行，亦正參考當年美國制裁伊朗時，當地銀行的應急方案。2019年年報顯示，四大國有內銀的美元計價負債高達1萬億美元（約7.8萬億港元），當中，中行的4330億美元（約3.37萬億港元）為各大行中最高。<br />\n<br />\n農業銀行（01288）傳亦正籌備應急方案，但該行的應對措施則相對溫和，現階段僅研究制裁名單一旦落實，如何找出受影響客戶，並要研究在不能取得美元資金的情況下，客戶潛在的流動性風險。<br />\n<br />\n消息又指出，國營租賃公司因為相當依賴美元貸款，故仍正為有關制裁謀後路，包括工行旗下工銀租賃和中國船舶租賃（03877）正就此作準備。<br />\n<br />\n路透引述一名熟悉制裁法的律師表示，《香港自治法案》具一定彈性可以限制銀行取得美元和參與美元結算，但亦不一定要強制執行，最終制裁的效力仍待法案公布更多有關細則。"},{"pid":"23e0053f961c1b79907be2fcc229740dfc23c7df","tid":2101608,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750547a995b22f02b22eabe2c0d629f6ede7cffc","tid":2101608,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"有大豆總統<br />\n<br />\n怕咩"},{"pid":"be9b15c5caecbcb0ef6004cb89886a2d71d9a846","tid":2101608,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:56:49.000Z","msg":"有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後咪又條係擠提<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590d38e263d16028acccbb8f8d67eb55f921eca9","tid":2101608,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"大家明啦"},{"pid":"e380ef9be51d095a6d9132f19bdd669ae5b2f7a6","tid":2101608,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"唔比用美元咪用歐元囉...<br />\n唔夠美鈔咪叫北韓印囉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c3f02092a7627ee807afe7ff757f31893ac76f","tid":2101608,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bf8d6c908af9ab929124d90f65b5ff22122959","tid":2101608,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e380ef9be51d095a6d9132f19bdd669ae5b2f7a6","tid":2101608,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"唔比用美元咪用歐元囉...<br />\n唔夠美鈔咪叫北韓印囉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:09:25.000Z","msg":"金仔真係印假美金高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6f1ca3c64b5ee23d44e36a44b8a8c4289c3bbb","tid":2101608,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"一定無事啦<br />\n中國大把錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff78d05efa27efad40f0cfdfaa0e5b68f37dca5","tid":2101608,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:11:45.000Z","msg":"都未劍指hsbc有撚用咩，全球最大洗黑錢銀行都唔制裁"}]}